//FINDING KIDDO-smallest child of a parent
//http://www.codechef.com/problems/ISM05

#include<iostream>
using namespace std;
int main(){
	int t,n,i,j,sum;
	cin>>t;
	while(t--){
		cin>>n;
		for(i=1;i<n;i++){
			j=i;
			sum=i;
			while(j){
				sum+=j%10;
				j/=10;
			}
			if(sum==n) break;
		}
		if(i==n) cout<<"NONE\n";
		else cout<<i<<endl;
	}
	return 0;
}
